summary:
Enthusiastic, positive professional working within the area of training and development with a passion for developing individuals.   Successful track record of project management  achieving outputs within time and budget. Proven record of team working, developing and leading others to deliver results. 
Decisive leadership, initiative and flexibility. 
Excellent communication skills, written and verbal
Outstanding organisational skills
Flexible and adaptable
Excellent IT skills
